CLOBBER
===

Clobber is an attempt to clone an obscure Windows game called Slay.

Clobber is approaching a playable state. No computer opponents are available, but it is possible to play local hotseat games against human opponents. Clobber is hosted at https://allknowingfrog.github.io/clobber

Completed:

Basic gui
Basic mouse input
Map generation (new map generated each game)
Turns (end turn by clicking the colored circle next to "Turn")
Troops (purchase, upgrade, move and attack, maintenance costs, starvation)
Indicators for active troops and regions with available troops
Merging and splitting regions (based on troop attacks)

Next steps:

Computer opponents
Trees?
